10:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Prepare a GAP analysis report to identify the areas which need maximum work for your laboratory,"}]
11:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025 consultants conduct a micro level survey for various essential parameters."}]
12:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO consultants in Dubai prepare all the essential documents as prescribed by the ISO certification bodies to achieve ISO 17025 certification."}]
13:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"We will provide necessary ISO training regarding ISO 17025 standards. Our ISO 17025 consultants prepare a detailed guidelines to ensure that all the ISO 17025 requirements are implemented throughout the organization."}]
14:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Our consultants will then conduct ISO internal audits with the help of ISO auditors to make sure that you are prepared for the ISO 17025 Certification."}]
15:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE and provides ISO consulting services in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. Wizms ISO consultant in Dubai offers top-class ISO consultancy services including ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO Certification audits in UAE."}]
16:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"If you also want to get your laboratory to get ISO 17025 certified, then get in touch with our ISO 17025 consultants today and let us partner you in your quest. Call us now."}]
